        "subject": "LU-6081 lib: add a full fledge JSON parser to liblustreapi",
        "message": "LU-6081 lib: add a full fledge JSON parser to liblustreapi\n\nThe migration data will be passed between lfs and the copytool in JSON\nformat. However Lustre has no decoder for JSON. liblustreapi has a\nJSON emitter but not a parser. cYAML also exists but is too limited;\nit cannot parse JSON nor handle arrays.\n\nImport the CCAN json parser/generator as-is\n(http://ccodearchive.net/info/json.html).\n\nLicence in MIT (X11).\n\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I31cf22cb01abf9c4213952db1aedaec2eae51698\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
